database - v1.1.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This library provides a really simple wrapper above PDO. It also eliminates
boilerplate associated with connecting to the database. It expects database
credentials to be managed in $GLOBALS.

The library also provides a simple Entity abstract class for wrapping UPDATE and
INSERT operations for single entities.

Primary authors:

    Roger Gee <roger.gee@tulsalibrary.org>

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
